34Dwarf_Signed
35dwarf_transform_to_disk_form(Dwarf_P_Debug dbg, Dwarf_Error *error)
36{
37
38 if (dbg == NULL) {
39 DWARF_SET_ERROR(dbg, error, DW_DLE_ARGUMENT);
40 return (DW_DLV_NOCOUNT);
41 }
42
43 if (_dwarf_generate_sections(dbg, error) != DW_DLE_NONE)
44 return (DW_DLV_NOCOUNT);
45
46 return (dbg->dbgp_seccnt);
47}

49Dwarf_Ptr
50dwarf_get_section_bytes(Dwarf_P_Debug dbg, Dwarf_Signed dwarf_section,
51 Dwarf_Signed *elf_section_index, Dwarf_Unsigned *length, Dwarf_Error *error)
52{
53 Dwarf_Ptr data;
54
55 (void) dwarf_section; /* ignored. */
56
57 if (dbg == NULL || elf_section_index == NULL || length == NULL) {
58 DWARF_SET_ERROR(dbg, error, DW_DLE_ARGUMENT);
59 return (NULL);
60 }
61
62 if (dbg->dbgp_secpos == NULL) {
63 DWARF_SET_ERROR(dbg, error, DW_DLE_NO_ENTRY);
64 return (NULL);
65 }
66
67 *elf_section_index = dbg->dbgp_secpos->ds_ndx;
68 *length = dbg->dbgp_secpos->ds_size;
69 data = dbg->dbgp_secpos->ds_data;
70
71 dbg->dbgp_secpos = STAILQ_NEXT(dbg->dbgp_secpos, ds_next);
72
73 return (data);
74}
